{"type": "article", "id": 10289, "title": "可以“砸”掉的混凝土灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-02T07:15:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235417Zz1lIDHKbAsdqV36.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这是罗马尼亚设计师 Dragos Motica 推出的一款混凝土灯饰，而你拿到它之后，可以自行决定要不要“砸”掉，创造出属于你自己的独一无二的新灯饰。灯饰采用的是圆柱形状，铁丝网外面包裹着混凝土，顶部为木质。购买灯饰你还将会获得一块石头，用来砸开混凝土，获得你的专属灯饰。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235413IFsW1kB67jXpuSRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354143kOCdxGvLBZi0sgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235414rKURgdj4JLsvymOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354154z1kVH3LEumXxlw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235415s0VUtmoN5b4rSZYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235415kgPxeZy8uCmAWMLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235416WEIzPXmKdlc6F0yh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}